<br>
In the boneyard (the area where the wizzie portal lands) there are several dragon skulls.  A wandering mob will pass directly over the top of one of them (it's one of the two closest to the zone wall and the long stone wall/fence thing).  I killed the drake that was the PH and was on my way.  The next spawn or two, ON the skull, was Mr. Old. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.thegeekhost.com/musician1993/gwenmay7.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=74894" target="top">Muse Gwenwyvar</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> ~ <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.frayedknot.net" target="top">Maestro of Frayed Knot</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub147.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=arune>Arune</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#330000>(6/1/03 3:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallstageleft.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=410.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> If your not high enough level for Song of Highsun, find a bard that is. Just get him to run through the area where he wonders highsunning mobs. Have someone waiting at the loc eqdiva gives. The mob will pop right on them.<br>
